  "3309290": {
    "name": "黑乌鸦",
    "steam_appid": 3309290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/998902006f3cd6c87251eb5aa32f89ed.avif?t=1771034796\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras_big/998902006f3cd6c87251eb5aa32f89ed.avif?t=1771034796 width=800 height=289 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black Raven </strong>《黑烏鴉》是一款基于斯拉夫都市神话的第三人称动作冒险游戏。故事设定在虚构的十四世纪乌克兰，将玩家带入黑死病肆虐的阴暗核心，穿越东欧广袤的平原和幽暗的森林。故事从一位朴实的农夫伊凡开始，他回家发现家人被掠夺者和邪恶的传说生物毁灭。充满复仇之心的他化身“黑鸦”，誓要追捕那些毁了他一生的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/8076f78a8042dec6c0b9951e8b9cd45c.poster.avif?t=1771034796\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/8076f78a8042dec6c0b9951e8b9cd45c.webm?t=1771034796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/8076f78a8042dec6c0b9951e8b9cd45c.mp4?t=1771034796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上幽灵般的旅程，穿越茂密的森林、被诅咒的战场和荒废的村庄，体验充满历史灵感的激烈战斗，对抗无情的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对各具特色的民间敌人，探索这片土地的秘密，感受伊凡在绝望和瘟疫笼罩的世界中的堕落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黑烏鴉》是乌克兰、波兰、俄罗斯和白俄罗斯文化的交融。以像素风格的艺术和历史主题为灵感，游戏呈现出难忘的愤怒、失落和决心的氛围。体验伊凡的坎坷之旅，从宁静的乡村走向阴暗的塔楼，直面最终的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/782ffb6b51bac6b12983808daec9be10.poster.avif?t=1771034796\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/782ffb6b51bac6b12983808daec9be10.webm?t=1771034796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/782ffb6b51bac6b12983808daec9be10.mp4?t=1771034796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的斯拉夫民间故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扣人心弦的剧情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剑术格斗系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态2.5D环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哥特式像素艺术</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阴暗的氛围音乐</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黑烏鴉》将玩家带入由文化历史和个人复仇塑造的世界，经历一场情感激烈、充满动作的旅程。准备化身“黑鸦”，面对复仇的最终代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/f206417f4eddf5c5f8f66ee04dd2b2da.poster.avif?t=1771034796\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/f206417f4eddf5c5f8f66ee04dd2b2da.webm?t=1771034796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309290/extras/f206417f4eddf5c5f8f66ee04dd2b2da.mp4?t=1771034796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
